com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters

Class ACDAddressListenerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters.AddressListenerAdapter
      • com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters.ACDAddressListenerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, AddressListener, ACDAddressListener

    public abstract class ACDAddressListenerAdapter
extends AddressListenerAdapter
implements ACDAddressListener
    An adapter which is notified of all changes to an ACDAddress object. The methods in this class are empty; this class is provided as a convenience for easily creating listeners by extending this class and overriding only the methods of interest.
    See Also:
    ACDAddressListener
